ke":1,"score":109,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:41:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200012/20/1220309.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200012%2F20%2F1220309.htm&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D7yOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=0d05bbf4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200012/20/1220309.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n最普遍的誤解，是公眾遊行必須得到警方批准。我希望所有議員現在明白，事實並非如此。《公安條例》只是就大部分超過30人的公眾遊行，訂立了一項通知警方的規定。<br />\n<br />\n警務處處長在接到舉行公眾遊行的意向通知後，除非反對舉行遊行，否則必須發出不反對通知書。如果處長在指定期限內沒有發出不反對通知書，也沒有發出反對遊行的通知，他便會被當作已發出不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">換言之，如果警方不發出反對通知，遊行便可進行，顯而易見，法例並無規定遊行必須得到警方批准。</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:49:02.000Z","msg":"望周知<br />\n出聲講反對囉怕你呀"},{"pid":"c064360ebe9b4a86cf0e88e2db752e85f8e98c35","tid":1362489,"uid":30635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:49:09.000Z","msg":"你發唔發我都會照出<br />\n唔出咪姐係淆班鄉黑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aee627952fb373a619383445273ad22974709b1","tid":1362489,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:50:44.000Z","msg":"姐係黑警怕咗18鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人哋出警告就跪低"},{"pid":"87a828102a6bb2b360d24f6d1263ca1834035a4c","tid":1362489,"uid":276633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:51:22.000Z","msg":"我去元朗行街姐<br />\n吾係咁都吾俾嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8114abaf75cf3838f301a532a1eb356186d5af18","tid":1362489,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:53:14.000Z","msg":"班警係咪驚自己比圍村佬打埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ba8b66cb49bb3e3c0dc6e5795f3e18f9324a63","tid":1362489,"uid